title: Affordable Sec. 42 Studio Apartment on the Blue Line!
posting_body: ['Studio/1 bath | $953-$965/month | 518-537 square feet | Income Limits Apply', "Located in one of Minneapolis' most rapidly evolving and vibrant communities, Longfellow is just steps from the light rail station, providing you with effortless convenience to shopping, dining, Downtown Minneapolis and Saint Paul, stadiums, the airport, and more.", 'Amenities include state of the art', 'fitness center, community room, underground heated parking, washer/dryer in unit, bicycle washing station, dog run, dog washing station, and balconies/patios (in select units).', 'Call today for more information!', 'show contact info', 'Find more information and the application at', '<URL>.', 'Neighborhood Amenities', 'Restaurants, Bars, Coffee Shops, and Fast Food', 'Light Rail 28th Street Station', 'Longfellow Park, Hiawatha School Park, Sibley Park, Lake Hiawatha, Minnehaha Falls, Mississippi River', 'Elementary School, High School, and more', 'Movie Theaters, Escape Rooms, Local Shopping, and more', 'Pet Friendly!', 'On-site dog run available', 'Dogs must be 30 pounds or less', 'Pet deposit required', 'One time pet fee', 'Rental Maximum Income Limits Apply to Some Homes:', '*Limits subject to change annually, call for details.', '*Affordable Section 42', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
